{"TopicId":159531,"ForumId":46,"TopicTitle":"Thread Starter Identification - Now with Image!","CreatedByName":"Speeding Mullet","CreatedById":62635,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-21T03:41:53Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Speeding Mullet","CreatedById":62635,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-21T03:41:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI was browsing a forum for a game recently, and noticed a pretty cool update that they\u0027ve made to the threads.\u00A0 Basically it identifies who the \u003Cabbr title=\u00221. Original Post(er). The first post in a thread, or the person who posted it. 2. Overpowered. A part or mechanic that upsets game balance by being too powerful.\u0022\u003EOP\u003C/abbr\u003E is.\u00A0 I think it helps identify \u003Cabbr title=\u00221. Original Post(er). The first post in a thread, or the person who posted it. 2. Overpowered. A part or mechanic that upsets game balance by being too powerful.\u0022\u003EOP\u003C/abbr\u003E in long threads, debates etc where it might not otherwise be clear.\u00A0 Also gives people a little sense of accountability when creating a thread.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ve mocked it up (horribly) for KSP below, and I thought it would be a nice thing to consider when next updating the forums.\u00A0 It\u0027s probably already been suggested but my cursory glance suggested it hadn\u0027t.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022SiV2UaF.jpg\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/SiV2UaF.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nInterested in thoughts!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSM\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-04-21T09:16:36Z\u0022 title=\u002204/21/2017 09:16  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EApril 21, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by Speeding Mullet\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003EAdded image\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cubinator","CreatedById":150330,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-22T23:50:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCool! Could be useful in those mod threads that are like 500 pages long.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"adsii1970","CreatedById":89014,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-22T23:51:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI like this idea! What about it, \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/12858-red-iron-crown/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002212858\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/12858-red-iron-crown/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Red Iron Crown\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dman979","CreatedById":123837,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-22T23:51:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI do want to point out that the \u003Cabbr title=\u00221. Original Post(er). The first post in a thread, or the person who posted it. 2. Overpowered. A part or mechanic that upsets game balance by being too powerful.\u0022\u003EOP\u003C/abbr\u003E is listed at the top of each page in the thread.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Speeding Mullet","CreatedById":62635,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-23T00:00:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223031076\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022159531\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221492905097\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022123837\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Dman979\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 minutes ago, Dman979 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI do want to point out that the \u003Cabbr title=\u00221. Original Post(er). The first post in a thread, or the person who posted it. 2. Overpowered. A part or mechanic that upsets game balance by being too powerful.\u0022\u003EOP\u003C/abbr\u003E is listed at the top of each page in the thread.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI know that the \u003Cabbr title=\u00221. Original Post(er). The first post in a thread, or the person who posted it. 2. Overpowered. A part or mechanic that upsets game balance by being too powerful.\u0022\u003EOP\u003C/abbr\u003E is listed at the top of the page of each thread, but when reading through huge threads it\u0027s a\u00A0nice QOL touch to be able to visually distinguish the \u003Cabbr title=\u00221. Original Post(er). The first post in a thread, or the person who posted it. 2. Overpowered. A part or mechanic that upsets game balance by being too powerful.\u0022\u003EOP\u003C/abbr\u003E\u0027s posts at a glance (or less).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI can\u00A0link you to the forum via PM\u00A0that I\u0027m talking about if you\u0027d like to see it in a \u0022live\u0022 setting? \u00A0I won\u0027t link it in this thread as said game has age advisory I think.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSM\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dman979","CreatedById":123837,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-23T00:01:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223031086\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022159531\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221492905634\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002262635\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Speeding Mullet\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, Speeding Mullet said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI can\u00A0link you to the forum via PM\u00A0that I\u0027m talking about if you\u0027d like to see it in a \u0022live\u0022 setting? \u00A0I won\u0027t link it in this thread as said game has age advisory I think.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNah, it\u0027s ok. Thanks for the offer, though. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Speeding Mullet","CreatedById":62635,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-23T00:03:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223031088\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022159531\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221492905690\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022123837\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Dman979\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, Dman979 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNah, it\u0027s ok. Thanks for the offer, though. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAll good! \u00A0I\u0027m interested in your thoughts while you are here though - Do you see the idea as having any negative effect, or can you see any reason why it wouldn\u0027t be a good thing to implement?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSM\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Red Iron Crown","CreatedById":12858,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-23T00:37:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223031091\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022159531\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221492905799\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002262635\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Speeding Mullet\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n28 minutes ago, Speeding Mullet said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents ipsClearfix\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDo you see the idea as having any negative effect, or can you see any reason why it wouldn\u0027t be a good thing to implement?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOne concern I would have is this: It\u0027s a misconception to think that threads belong to the OPs. Threads belong to the community, and the \u003Cabbr title=\u00221. Original Post(er). The first post in a thread, or the person who posted it. 2. Overpowered. A part or mechanic that upsets game balance by being too powerful.\u0022\u003EOP\u003C/abbr\u003E doesn\u0027t have special privileges in them, aside from the mods offering the courtesy of closing threads upon request. A tag marking the \u003Cabbr title=\u00221. Original Post(er). The first post in a thread, or the person who posted it. 2. Overpowered. A part or mechanic that upsets game balance by being too powerful.\u0022\u003EOP\u003C/abbr\u003E would reinforce this misconception.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI could see the feature being useful though, especially in gameplay questions and the support forums.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dman979","CreatedById":123837,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-23T00:42:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223031091\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022159531\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221492905799\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002262635\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Speeding Mullet\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n16 minutes ago, Speeding Mullet said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAll good! \u00A0I\u0027m interested in your thoughts while you are here though - Do you see the idea as having any negative effect, or can you see any reason why it wouldn\u0027t be a good thing to implement?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes, I can see it having a slight negative effect.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSometimes, when an \u003Cabbr title=\u00221. Original Post(er). The first post in a thread, or the person who posted it. 2. Overpowered. A part or mechanic that upsets game balance by being too powerful.\u0022\u003EOP\u003C/abbr\u003E starts a thread, they think they have total control over it. This is not true. They have some control, but to a point. My feeling- \u003Cstrong\u003Eand let me be clear, I\u0027m speaking for \u003Cem\u003Emyself\u003C/em\u003E and not the Moderation team\u003C/strong\u003E- is that this will encourage something like this, acting as a \u0022badge\u0022 of authority.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDarn it, Red ninja\u0027d me.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Frybert","CreatedById":97766,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-23T00:44:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223031125\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022159531\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221492908130\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022123837\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Dman979\u0022\u003E\n\u003